{
  "stem": "13219.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they took all the men-- able men-- about 12 or 14 of us, and then all the women and kids, and they gave us rifles, each one, each man.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they said that you should do by yourself, because we can't do, and they-- we-- they separated us, and the kids, and the women, themselves.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they went their own way until the liberation when the Russians came in.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, this was 1943.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This would have, by now, brought you well into the spring of '43.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was the spring.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To our group?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had-- the elder-- the older man was the leader.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, the partisan, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The name was Medvedev-- Medvedev.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's like, a bear in Russia is Medvedev.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was a very handsome, nice man.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Was very-- he was very nice.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was a colonel in the military.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I know, because when he-- when, after the war, we knew about it, because one of the women from our city-- her name was [NON-ENGLISH], who was there, has-- she was very friendly with him.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when he left she couldn't go with him because they told her that he's married.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But then she went to Russia--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She stayed with her father and two brothers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Her father died, but they came to Israel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I met her in Boston, I think in 1960, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I think '60, something like this.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At that time he was a hero, yes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, I think so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he spared a lot of Jewish lives.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Among the Righteous Gentiles, I consider the woman who saved my life, the man who took me through the city while the pogrom was going.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "About the righteous-- him, I consider, yes.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
